Invoicing
Last updated December 23rd, 2025

Overview
The Invoicing API enables merchants to generate invoices and receive payments from customers through one-time payments, installment plans, and auto debits (MTN and Telecel only) using:

Mobile Money
Bank Card
Wallet (G-Money)
Cash / Cheque

Invoicing

Invoicing

Invoicing

With a single integration, you can accept one-time, installment, and automated debit payments on your application. Provide the customer's debit details and Hubtel will manage the scheduling and processing of payments.

The following provides an overview of the REST API endpoints for interacting programmatically with the Hubtel Invoicing API within your application.



Getting Started

Understanding the Service Flow
The Hubtel Invoicing API includes three main API endpoints which can be used to create an invoice. They are:

Pay At Once: This endpoint allows you to create an invoice for your customer to make a full one-time payment. Available payment channels include mobile money, debit/credit card and G-Money.
Pay In Installments: This endpoint allows you to create an invoice for your customer to make payment for the total amount, either in full or through partial payments.
Auto Debit: This endpoint allows you to create an invoice for your customer to make payment for the total amount, in smaller automated payments until the specified due date.


API Reference

Pay at Once
To initiate a Pay at Once request, send an HTTP POST request to the below URL with the required parameters. It’s also mandatory to pass your Hubtel POS Sales ID for Create Invoice requests in the endpoint. Find your POS Sales ID here.


API Endpoint	https://invoicing.hubtel.com/api/invoice/{POS_SALES_ID}/pay-at-once
Request Type	POST
Content Type	JSON

REQUEST PARAMETERS
Parameter	Type	Requirement	Description
invoiceNumber	String	Mandatory	The invoice number associated with the invoice. It must not be empty and should be a maximum of 20 characters in length.
customerName	String	Mandatory	The name of the customer.
callbackUrl	String	Mandatory	The callback URL expected to receive the final status of the payment.
customerPhoneNumber	String	Mandatory	The phone number of the customer. Customer will receive invoice via this number.
customerEmail	String	Optional	This refers to the email of the customer. Customer will receive invoice via this email.
hasTax	Boolean	Optional	This indicates whether tax will be added to the invoice.
IssuedBy	String	Mandatory	This refers to the person or staff creating the invoice.
createdBy	String	Mandatory	This refers to the person or staff creating the invoice.
dueDate	DateTime	Mandatory	This refers to the due date for payment.
note	String	Optional	This is a brief description about the invoice.
reminders	ArrayOfObjects	Mandatory	This helps send reminders to customers about making payment for the invoice created.
isBefore	Boolean	Mandatory	This indicates whether reminders should be sent before or after the due date.
days	Integer	Mandatory	This indicates the frequency at which the reminders should be sent.
items	ArrayOfObjects	Mandatory	This helps schedule the one-time payment.
description	String	Mandatory	A brief description of the payment being made.
quantity	String	Mandatory	The quantity of the items being purchased
unitPrice	Float	Mandatory	The cost for the item being purchased.

RESPONSE PARAMETERS
Parameter	Type	Description
message	String	A brief message indicating the success or failure of the invoice creation.
code	Number	The status code
Data	ArrayOfObject	An object containing the required data response from the Invoicing API.
InvoiceId	String	A unique identifier for the generated invoice
paymentUrl	String	Payments can be made via this URL.

SAMPLE REQUEST
HTTP

copy
Copy
POST /api/invoice/11684/pay-at-once HTTP/1.1 
Host: invoicing.hubtel.com 
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic endjeOBiZHhza24=
Cache-Control: no-cache

{
  "invoiceNumber": "test23",
  "customerName": "John",
  "customerPhoneNumber": "024000000",
  "customerEmail": "rse@gmail.com",
  "hasTax": true,
  "issuedBy": "John",
  "createdBy": "John",
  "dueDate": "2025-03-18T11:20:23.147Z",
  "isDefault": true,
  "callbackUrl": "https://webhook.site/40b08e13-05f2-4892-8709-fe379878e6be",
  "note": "Pay at Once",
  "reminders": [
      {
          "days": 5,
          "isBefore": true
      }
  ],
  "items": [
      {
          "description": "Test Invoice",
          "quantity": 1,
          "unitPrice": 0.01
      }
  ]
}

SAMPLE RESPONSE
200 OK

copy
Copy
{
  "message": "Invoice Created Successfully",
  "code": 200,
  "data": {
      "invoiceId": "hA344ftcBZ",
      "paymentUrl": "https://invdebit.com/hA344ftcBZ"
      }
}


