Retry
The Retry API enables you to retry failed auto debit payments.

To initiate an Retry request, send an HTTP POST request to the below URL with the required parameters. It’s also mandatory to pass your Hubtel POS Sales ID for Auto Debit requests in the endpoint. Find your POS Sales ID here.


API Endpoint	https://invoicing.hubtel.com/api/invoice/{POS_SALES_ID}/payments/{PaymentDetailId}/retry
Request Type	POST
Content Type	JSON

REQUEST PARAMETERS
Parameter	Type	Requirement	Description
POS_SALES_ID	String	Mandatory	The POS_SALES_ID associated with your account
PaymentDetailId	String	Mandatory	The PaymentDetailId that is returned in the callback.

RESPONSE PARAMETERS
Parameter	Type	Description
message	String	A brief description of the request status.
code	Object	The status code.
data	String	Always "null".

SAMPLE REQUEST
HTTP

copy
Copy
POST /api/invoice/11684/payments/98a9fd4a-47f3-4709-8c4f-fb89465fcf51/retry HTTP/1.1 
Host: invoicing.hubtel.com 
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic endjeOBiZHhza24=
Cache-Control: no-cache

SAMPLE RESPONSE
200 OK

copy
Copy
{
  "message": "Payment retry has been initiated. Check invoice status for confirmation.",
  "code": 200,
  "data": null
}


